pageContext.claim: “Comey testified (under oath) that it was a “unanimous” decision on Crooked Hillary. Lisa Page transcripts show he LIED. @jasoninthehouse”
pageContext.analysis: The Page transcripts do not show that Comey misled anyone about the decision not to prosecute Hillary Clinton. Several former officials have outlined why Comey made the decisions that he did. Page's transcripts did show that some members of the FBI engaged in "smack talk" about Clinton, but that's different than recommending prosecution.
